687
00:48:49,692 --> 00:48:51,191
I've been doing a lot of thinking to figure out...

688
00:48:51,192 --> 00:48:52,362
how we ended up like this.

689
00:48:55,572 --> 00:48:56,741
And I've concluded...

690
00:49:03,621 --> 00:49:05,792
