702
00:50:08,351 --> 00:50:09,391
I...

703
00:50:17,072 --> 00:50:18,072
I feel like...

704
00:50:19,862 --> 00:50:22,661
I ruined you when you were so kind and bright.

705
00:50:27,752 --> 00:50:28,911
I'm so sorry.

706
00:50:35,882 --> 00:50:38,261
Thank you for living with me for six years.

707
00:50:40,681 --> 00:50:42,391
I'll live well from now on.

708
00:50:46,181 --> 00:50:47,351
