753
00:53:55,241 --> 00:53:56,581
Stop talking nonsense and come to my house.

754
00:53:56,911 --> 00:53:58,911
The kids say they want to blow out the candles with you.

755
00:53:59,081 --> 00:54:00,461
Sung Ji, do you want to talk to Auntie?

756
00:54:00,462 --> 00:54:03,172
Can't you hear me? I said I was with my friends.

757
00:54:03,712 --> 00:54:06,342
Are you really? You're not going to mope around, are you?

758
00:54:07,092 --> 00:54:08,132
No.

759
00:54:08,471 --> 00:54:10,971
- I'm hanging up. Bye. - Hey, wait.

760
00:54:22,862 --> 00:54:23,902
